With the included LED bulbs, you can set up your table lamp right away and enjoy its cozy illumination.

❤【Customer Satisfaction】Our goal is to serve every customer and try our best to provide you with excellent service. manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: RORIANO Vintage Farmhouse Table Lamp with Night Light for Living Room Bedroom Set of 2 RORIANO Farmhouse Table Lamp, boasting an exquisitely crafted exterior design. Its gentle illumination casts a soft and comforting glow, catering to your desires, whether unwinding during leisurely moments or engaging in focused work or study sessions.Experience the epitome of aesthetic refinement and practical functionality with the RORIANO table lamp.
